div(layout="row")
  div(layout="column")
    md-content(layout-padding)
      form(id="edit-profile-form" name="editProfileForm" ng-submit="updateProfile(editProfileForm)")
        h2(id="edit-profile-info") Edit Profile Info
        p(class="profileChangeNotice") If you don't make any changes to a field confirm changes will do nothing.
        p(class="profileChangeNotice") You can also click outside of the window to exit.
        br
        md-input-container
          label Change Email
          input(name="newEmail" type="email" ng-model="user.newEmail")
        md-input-container
          label Change Password
          input(name="newPassword" type="password" minlength="8" ng-model="user.newPassword")
        md-input-container
          label Confirm Change of Password
          input(name="changeConfirm" type="password" ng-model="user.newPasswordConfirm")       
        br
        md-button(type="submit" class="md-raised md-primary confirm" value="Sign Up") Confirm Changes
